strings: <voice_0x01000A27><se_high>Reflections: open the door This is a special door that only Alessandro can open.
<voice_0x01000A28><se_high>Reflections: If you don't believe, give it a try.
<se_def>Even if I pull the door or remove it, it won't budge. in brief<:>
<voice_0x01000A29><se_high>Reflections: I told you! Only Alexandra knows how to open this door.
<voice_0x01000A30><se_high>Reflections: You seem to believe me, but I don't. deplore.
<voice_0x01000A2A><se_high>Reflections: because it's urgent, I need to teach you how to open the door. But you have to promise not to tell anyone.
<voice_0x01000A2F><se_high>Reflections: this is my job I have returned to the stage. Please help Jessica!
